data.description: This stunning three bedroom three bath townhome, just a year old, offers breathtaking views of the mountains. The exterior of the townhome has a modern design. As you enter the home, you'll immediately notice the open concept living space and natural light.The primary bedroom is located on the second floor and features a large walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom with a double vanity and a large shower. The second and third bedrooms are also generously sized, each with their own full bathroom just across the hall. Additionally, this townhome features a laundry room on the second floor, a two-car garage, and a private outdoor space perfect for relaxing. This home is Located in a desirable neighborhood with easy access to hiking and biking trails, as well as shopping, dining, and entertainment options. This townhome offers the perfect balance of outdoor living and city convenience.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful townhome your new home! Schedule a showing today to experience the stunning mountain views and modern low patience living space for yourself.
